<p class="h1">HALAH</p>
<p class="fl">Place in Assyria where the inhabitants of Samaria were taken after its fall in 722 <span class="era">BC</span> (<a href="?bref=2Kgs.17.6">2 Kgs 17:6</a>; <a href="?bref=2Kgs.18.11">18:11</a>; cf. <a href="?bref=1Chr.5.26">1 Chr 5:26</a>).</p>
